answers.answer: If you have any other metal in your mouth? Or have metal crowns? KNOW what's in your mouth & Immediately get a "Scratch" test by a dermatologist & if you can afford it, get a blood test with one of 3 companieshttp://www.melisa.orghttp://www.biocomplaboratories.com/biocompatibility-Testing-Dental-Toxicity.htmlhttp://www.ccrlab.comGood Luck, I wasn't so lucky!!
